h1: Playing Bass on Social Media Part Dos
para1: Yea my last blog was a little naive. A while of posting on social media has now got me in a nervous mess. In the words of Radiohead - I lost myself.
para2: I moved the majority of my videos to only me or friends only. I can't even pinpoint what it is, just an accumulation of stuff. I thought I'll just get better and join some courses.
para3: So I start some technique stuff on slapping as part of that, then I start sounding like an absolute newbie at slapping so my paranoia explodes!
